up?title=MR+imaging+of+focal+hepatic+injury+due+to+use+of+surgical+retractors&amp;author=JP+Earls&amp;author=GA+Krinsky&amp;author=DR+DeCorato&amp;publication_year=1996&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=816-817&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.167.3.8751708&amp;pmid=8751708">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Yassa NA, Peters JH. CT of focal hepatic injury due to surgical retractor. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 1996; 166(3):599–602.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/ajr.166.3.8623634">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8623634/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=CT+of+focal+hepatic+injury+due+to+surgical+retractor&amp;author=NA+Yassa&amp;author=JH+Peters&amp;publication_year=1996&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=599-602&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.166.3.8623634&amp;pmid=8623634">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">8.</div><div id="r8" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Acosta JM, Tiao G, Stein JE, Mahour GH. Temporary relocation of testes to the anterior abdominal wall before radiation therapy of the pelvis or perineum. <em>J Pediatr Surg</em> 2002;37(8):1232–1233.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1053/jpsu.2002.34488">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12149714/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Temporary+relocation+of+testes+to+the+anterior+abdominal+wall+before+radiation+therapy+of+the+pelvis+or+perineum&amp;author=JM